{"tid":1228511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 聽日遊行有咩辦法可以提高士氣？","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:40:08.000Z","uid":233541,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb7523685898ab441a05cf67144bca8047a966f","tid":1228511,"uid":233541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:15:30.000Z","msg":"其實上次6.9個陣一路行 一路都好想嗌下<br />\n無奈揸咪既 一時upup下 一時又勸人捐錢<br />\n就算嗌口號 都有啲1999<br />\n嗌左幾聲&quot;香港人...加油&quot; 無預兆地轉左&quot;林鄭...&quot;<br />\n好彩醒目識轉嗌&quot;下台&quot;  嗌左加油真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要自摑十巴<br />\n(當然 都有聽到人嗌&quot;林鄭...仆街&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以 我覺得如果有一set大家<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有共識 集中嗌既口號</span></span><br />\n清清晰晰咁話比呢個世界知 我地行出黎既訴求<br />\n身邊既大家同聲同氣  同路人意志更堅定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至可以加上啲拍手既節奏<br />\n好似啲人睇波打氣個陣咁 <br />\n或者queens既we will rock you咁<br />\n想像下一百萬人一齊拍既個種聲勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(又可以比把聲抖一抖 始終齋嗌好攰 維持唔到好耐)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">揸咪：林鄭月娥下台 (拍-拍-拍拍)<br />\n大家：林鄭月娥下台 (拍-拍-拍拍)<br />\n揸咪：撒回送中條例 (拍-拍-拍拍)<br />\n大家：撒回送中條例 (拍-拍-拍拍)<br />\n揸咪：追究黑警責任 (拍-拍-拍拍)<br />\n大家：追究黑警責任 (拍-拍-拍拍)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有無咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19418707ddd0daf2d111c8ab1b9bed9fc74c716c","tid":1228511,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"撤回修例<br />\n全面取消之前暴動罪<br />\n林鄭 李 鄭 盧必須辭職<br />\n全民普選"},{"pid":"593021691a3d858d752a909360340cfefffddcea","tid":1228511,"uid":233541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:03:58.000Z","msg":"(輕輕一推)"},{"pid":"90ff25636be403649981bb2879087871b1ae5450","tid":1228511,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:09:43.000Z","msg":"有無方法可以增加下大家嘅mp值？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a6ecde8c5522e28fe9bfd6d6b84fb087a9d11d","tid":1228511,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:10:55.000Z","msg":"不撤！<br />\n不散！"},{"pid":"44ec959d309ac7957df4faa38a89b162baf80692","tid":1228511,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:36:52.000Z","msg":"你條三毛狗潛水潛左去邊<br />\n<br />\n比機會你解釋下都唔出黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪屋企人過身唔得閒？？？"},{"pid":"c76bc43f4076b4cffce441384fd355f25ab05cb4","tid":1228511,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44ec959d309ac7957df4faa38a89b162baf80692","tid":1228511,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:36:52.000Z","msg":"你條三毛狗潛水潛左去邊<br />\n<br />\n比機會你解釋下都唔出黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪屋企人過身唔得閒？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"覆錯人唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a714326ce65dc29628e2485a00ecf6847cc313c3","tid":1228511,"uid":233541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c76bc43f4076b4cffce441384fd355f25ab05cb4","tid":1228511,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44ec959d309ac7957df4faa38a89b162baf80692","tid":1228511,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:36:52.000Z","msg":"你條三毛狗潛水潛左去邊<br />\n<br />\n比機會你解釋下都唔出黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\